commandText:
SELECT c1."Id", c1."CreatedDateTime", c1."UserId", s."Id", s."Amount", s."CartId", s."OrderId", s."ProductId", s."Id0", s."Cost", s."Descriprion", s."ImageUrl", s."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedDateTime", c."UserId"
    FROM "Carts" AS c
    WHERE c."UserId" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS c1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Descriprion", p."ImageUrl", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItem" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON c1."Id" = s."CartId"
ORDER BY c1."Id", s."Id"

commandText:
SELECT c1."Id", c1."CreatedDateTime", c1."UserId", s."Id", s."Amount", s."CartId", s."OrderId", s."ProductId", s."Id0", s."Cost", s."Descriprion", s."ImageUrl", s."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedDateTime", c."UserId"
    FROM "Carts" AS c
    WHERE c."UserId" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS c1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Descriprion", p."ImageUrl", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItem" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON c1."Id" = s."CartId"
ORDER BY c1."Id", s."Id"

commandText:
SELECT c1."Id", c1."CreatedDateTime", c1."UserId", s."Id", s."Amount", s."CartId", s."OrderId", s."ProductId", s."Id0", s."Cost", s."Descriprion", s."ImageUrl", s."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedDateTime", c."UserId"
    FROM "Carts" AS c
    WHERE c."UserId" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS c1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Descriprion", p."ImageUrl", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItem" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON c1."Id" = s."CartId"
ORDER BY c1."Id", s."Id"

commandText:
SELECT c1."Id", c1."CreatedDateTime", c1."UserId", s."Id", s."Amount", s."CartId", s."OrderId", s."ProductId", s."Id0", s."Cost", s."Descriprion", s."ImageUrl", s."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedDateTime", c."UserId"
    FROM "Carts" AS c
    WHERE c."UserId" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS c1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Descriprion", p."ImageUrl", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItem" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON c1."Id" = s."CartId"
ORDER BY c1."Id", s."Id"
